Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Card Was Mailed To Me

If you do not receive your card by July 2, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request that we send your new card to you.
